{"tid":861654,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"(必入)想做孝子買張按摩椅 求推介！","createTime":"2018-10-14T09:55:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-16T11:43:27.000Z","uid":115614,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"1755b7718d1d3299d2cf0bf992237e2cd6bc7144","tid":861654,"uid":115614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T09:55:56.000Z","msg":"事關家母年紀越黎越大 腰肩頸都開始唔聽話<br />\n所以小弟想入手一部按摩椅孝順下家母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係市面上太多選擇 但又怕買錯 因為好少按摩椅評價<br />\n小弟都出過去試過osix otx ogawx 都好似唔錯咁<br />\n有無屋企有按摩椅既巴打絲打比個建議參考下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n感激不盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\nogawx e神個部自己都幾喜歡 但怕有更好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b065589265c0434b305f7b03cbd08629f520001","tid":861654,"uid":115614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T05:25:59.000Z","msg":"yo"},{"pid":"5262177107591d568c018162dc7737089a03c2fc","tid":861654,"uid":115614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T05:26:12.000Z","msg":"有無人呀"},{"pid":"b6bf14a296fde841ce176962a9faad583bbf6291","tid":861654,"uid":115614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T05:26:35.000Z","msg":"yo"},{"pid":"3954c90485557d7992a13268dcf30ddbfc9659c6","tid":861654,"uid":115614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T05:26:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f2dfad07d2212f16bcb24d0128e2e04c2194f07","tid":861654,"uid":152266,"